oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: County jail men
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Interior of the county jail. Men are posed barefoot in their suits to protest the epithet "Hillbilly." (L to R) Hugh Standifer, Clarence Harmon, Bob Robinson, A. J. Green and Harry Haynes.
